WEBVTT

00:00:06.047 --> 00:00:11.221
I’m sitting here this afternoon with Shri Mataji Nirmala Devi.

00:00:11.302 --> 00:00:12.995
Is that how I say your name, Shri Mataji?

00:00:13.075 --> 00:00:15.173
That’s correct, it’s correct.

00:00:15.293 --> 00:00:18.453
Shri Mataji is a world-renowned spiritual leader,

00:00:18.533 --> 00:00:20.933
and we’re very happy to welcome you here today.

00:00:21.013 --> 00:00:22.732
Thank you very much.

00:00:22.813 --> 00:00:27.093
Shri Mataji. Can you tell us when you first realized

00:00:27.173 --> 00:00:30.453
that you had this special spiritual gift?

00:00:34.026 --> 00:00:39.532
You see, it’s like this, that when we are bornp
as human beings, we know we are human beings.

00:00:39.613 --> 00:00:46.269
In the same way, I knew from my very birth that I was something of that kind.

00:00:47.373 --> 00:00:52.045
And since you’ve been a young person, you’ve been spreading

00:00:52.126 --> 00:00:59.012
this spiritual message, or is this something that you’ve just recently begun to do?

00:00:59.093 --> 00:01:03.932
No, I had to wait and see certain things about human beings.

00:01:04.013 --> 00:01:10.232
Because I had to study why human beings cannot get Realization en masse.

00:01:10.312 --> 00:01:12.413
They should get it en masse, otherwise,

00:01:12.493 --> 00:01:15.293
if one person gets it, then people don’t understand them.

00:01:15.373 --> 00:01:19.212
They crucify them, they poison them, they’ve tortured them.

00:01:19.293 --> 00:01:23.893
So why shouldn’t it work out en masse? And so, I had to study

00:01:23.974 --> 00:01:27.692
for years together. At the age of my 47th year,

00:01:27.773 --> 00:01:35.892
I discovered a method by which Self-realization can be achieved en masse.

00:01:35.973 --> 00:01:39.093
Shri Mataji, you use the term Self-realization.

00:01:39.173 --> 00:01:42.653
That’s a term we’re not really very familiar with here in America.

00:01:42.733 --> 00:01:45.253
Can you explain that to me?

00:01:45.373 --> 00:01:50.172
It’s the same as what Christ has said that, “You are to be born again”.

00:01:50.292 --> 00:01:54.892
That is when, like a bird, you see, you are an egg,

00:01:54.973 --> 00:01:57.509
and then you become a bird.

00:01:57.589 --> 00:02:02.085
And also a bird is called a ‘twice-born’ in Sanskrit language.

00:02:02.165 --> 00:02:08.372
In the same way, a human being is bound by his conditioning, by his ego,

00:02:08.453 --> 00:02:16.677
but when he is born again, then he is called as a
Self-realized person,

00:02:16.757 --> 00:02:20.744
because he knows about himself, about his inner being.

00:02:20.824 --> 00:02:26.972
And also he’s endowed on his central nervous system with a new awareness

00:02:27.053 --> 00:02:32.212
that Jung had described as Collective Consciousness.

00:02:32.293 --> 00:02:36.972
So it’s not just a certificate one can give that you are baptized,

00:02:37.053 --> 00:02:41.532
or you are Self-realized, or you are twice-born.

00:02:41.613 --> 00:02:46.453
It’s a living process, which is the last breakthrough

00:02:46.534 --> 00:02:50.694
in your awareness, where you become.

00:02:50.774 --> 00:02:52.287
It’s a question of becoming.

00:02:52.367 --> 00:02:58.919
You become a personality which can feel the All-pervading Power,

00:02:58.999 --> 00:03:05.732
about which every scripture has described, on your central nervous system.

00:03:05.813 --> 00:03:09.972
This is what we call as ‘bodh’, as in Buddha,

00:03:10.053 --> 00:03:14.453
called as ‘Veda’, as in Veda. Means you have to know it

00:03:14.533 --> 00:03:18.733
on your central nervous system, on your fingertips,

00:03:18.813 --> 00:03:23.373
as Mohammed Sahib has said that, “You have to know it on your fingertips”

00:03:23.453 --> 00:03:31.692
that it exists all around you, like a very beautiful, soothing, cool breeze.

00:03:31.773 --> 00:03:34.773
This is the cool breeze of the Holy Ghost.

00:03:34.893 --> 00:03:37.853
So Shri Mataji, what you are describing then,

00:03:37.933 --> 00:03:42.213
is a process that comes from inside each of us,

00:03:42.293 --> 00:03:46.052
and is something that everyone can feel,
or just a few people?

00:03:46.133 --> 00:03:51.429
No, everybody can feel. ‘Sahaja’, you see, we call it a Sahaja Yoga.

00:03:51.523 --> 00:03:54.292
Sahaja means born with you.

00:03:54.373 --> 00:03:59.563
It is born with you, this yoga,

00:03:59.643 --> 00:04:02.994
or we can say this promise of yoga is born with you.

00:04:03.074 --> 00:04:05.732
It means there is a power within you,

00:04:05.813 --> 00:04:09.212
which is called in Sanskrit language as Kundalini,

00:04:09.293 --> 00:04:14.332
which resides in the triangular bone, which, surprisingly,

00:04:14.413 --> 00:04:18.973
the Greeks called as sacrum bone.
That means they knew it’s a sacred bone.

00:04:19.053 --> 00:04:23.283
And this is the fourth power which resides within us,

00:04:23.453 --> 00:04:30.293
and which somehow or other awakened, pierces through your fontanel bone area,

00:04:30.413 --> 00:04:38.453
and you really get the experience of actualization of your second birth,

00:04:38.533 --> 00:04:43.493
by feeling the cool breeze coming out of your head, you yourself.

00:04:43.573 --> 00:04:46.733
And you can experience it on your fingertips.

00:04:46.813 --> 00:04:51.628
It’s not just imagination. You have to certify yourself.

00:04:52.252 --> 00:04:55.812
Well Shri Mataji, It sounds extremely simple.

00:04:55.893 --> 00:05:00.013
How does one have this feeling coming from their fingertips,

00:05:00.093 --> 00:05:03.053
and a cool breeze coming from the top of the head?

00:05:03.133 --> 00:05:10.533
Everything vital has to be simple. See how a seed sprouts.

00:05:10.613 --> 00:05:12.732
They have to just put it in the Mother Earth.

00:05:12.813 --> 00:05:16.332
The Mother Earth has got the capacity to sprout it,

00:05:16.413 --> 00:05:20.573
and the seed has all the built-in machinery in it.

00:05:20.653 --> 00:05:23.533
In the same way, you too have everything within you,

00:05:23.613 --> 00:05:25.652
and it just sprouts.

00:05:25.733 --> 00:05:30.453
So Shri Mataji, once this is sprouted, then what?

00:05:30.533 --> 00:05:34.213
What happens to me? Do I become different?

00:05:34.333 --> 00:05:40.133
You start transforming completely, because you get the light.

00:05:40.253 --> 00:05:45.153
When there is no light, you can catch hold of a snake
thinking it’s a rope.

00:05:45.233 --> 00:05:48.575
But when there’s light, you can see it yourself
and you drop it.

00:05:48.722 --> 00:05:51.722
Well, the transforming power that you describe, then,

00:05:51.802 --> 00:05:56.322
is something that once it happens to me, I keep it for myself.

00:05:56.402 --> 00:06:01.042
Can I give this transformation power to my friends or my relatives?

00:06:01.122 --> 00:06:02.442
Or is it just mine?

00:06:02.522 --> 00:06:06.042
No, no, of course. A light which is lightened

00:06:06.122 --> 00:06:08.962
is not kept under the table, as Christ has told.

00:06:09.042 --> 00:06:11.162
In the same way, when you are enlightened,

00:06:11.242 --> 00:06:14.682
you can enlighten other people. You are endowed with that power.

00:06:14.762 --> 00:06:18.035
You have those powers, then you can do it.

00:06:18.481 --> 00:06:23.521
Because it passes through your seven subtle, six subtle centres,

00:06:23.602 --> 00:06:31.481
and pierces through your last center of limbic area, which is nourished,

00:06:31.562 --> 00:06:35.029
which is being made knowledgeable.

00:06:35.109 --> 00:06:39.762
So when you start giving this to others,

00:06:39.842 --> 00:06:44.162
you can feel the centres of other people on your fingertips,

00:06:44.242 --> 00:06:48.722
and you know what is their problem. Only thing, if you have to know,

00:06:48.802 --> 00:06:54.882
only if you can know, how to get rid of those obstacles

00:06:54.962 --> 00:06:59.026
of these subtle centres, you can manage it.

00:06:59.236 --> 00:07:04.574
So what you’re saying is once this power is awakened in each of us,

00:07:04.654 --> 00:07:10.082
then the normal problems of humanity, the problems of health

00:07:10.162 --> 00:07:16.722
or stress or of nervousness will go away?

00:07:16.802 --> 00:07:18.495
That’s the minimum.

00:07:18.575 --> 00:07:20.382
There is more?

00:07:20.462 --> 00:07:26.120
That’s the minimum that would happen. It cures so many incurable diseases.

00:07:27.453 --> 00:07:32.228
And it also gives you better peace.

00:07:32.308 --> 00:07:36.885
It has cured many mental cases.

00:07:36.965 --> 00:07:42.501
People have got rid of many drug habits, alcoholism,

00:07:42.581 --> 00:07:47.817
because, as I told you, you see the snake and you drop it.

00:07:47.897 --> 00:07:51.677
Also you become very powerful but not aggressive, very compassionate.